=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＊Character＊</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421410/extras/efd8898594395ff569180b96cd98f5a8.avif?t=1769673619\" width=358 height=337 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hatsune, a cute goddess.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She is very interested in human food.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＊Game Features＊</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple classic RPG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy gameplay without fighting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch the story of evil spirits</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes some voice acting and sound effects</p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>＊Story＊</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All over the world, there are well-known haunted places, and one of them is particularly eye-catching and dangerous...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That place is the &quot;Haunted House&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many people have been abused there, but even the police are helpless about the ghosts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The troubled people involved decided to hire an exorcist to expel the evil spirits,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But after the exorcism, they found that the evil spirits here are very powerful, and all the spells don't work!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finally, the frustrated exorcists decided to go to the shrine to ask the goddess for help—</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thus, the goddess's exorcism mission begins!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>＊How to play＊</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3421410/extras/8f39a17b6814efde24ef794c9e04548b.avif?t=1769673619\" width=800 height=612 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲Explore the map</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><